EKURHULENI - Living to a hundred years is regarded as a milestone achievement but granny Malesole Mokoena will turn 121 years next month. The centenarian wished for a special get-together with her closest and the Ekurhuleni municipality made her wish come true. With years of life experiences behind her Mokoena is offering some wise words to the youth. eNCA reporter Khayelihle Khumalo has the full report in the video gallery above. eNCA